description:
Support the next Constitutional Amendment and save American democracy!

Liberty Cookies is a supplier of patriotic fundraising products and the home of the Stars and Stripes Forever infinity USA flag.  Our target market is high school civic classes fundraising their field trips to Washington DC and Philadelphia.  We also provide affiliate links for supporters of democracy. 

Donations to the ConstitutionalDAO project will be used to promote the IRL patriotic products, bootstrap affiliates, and sponsor activists in select local markets.
